    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/a2012c0b29dddd916f1e810345904aa7.poster.avif?t=1746038470\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/a2012c0b29dddd916f1e810345904aa7.webm?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/a2012c0b29dddd916f1e810345904aa7.mp4?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Blood Punk</strong> is a hyper violent fast-paced retro FPS where you must exchange your health for bullets.<br><br>Eviscerate giant abominations with the blood of an angel using deadly weapons in a dark fantasy comic book world.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/38e773683ca2fa4172d71b52d6d454e9.poster.avif?t=1746038470\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/38e773683ca2fa4172d71b52d6d454e9.webm?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/38e773683ca2fa4172d71b52d6d454e9.mp4?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The world was in balance, but the greed of a monarch led him down a treacherous path. <br>He ensnared an angel and exchanged it's divine ichor with his own mortal blood. <br><br>The balance was broken and the world fell into desolation. <br><br>Now it is up to Numa, scion of the deluded monarch, with celestial blood coursing through her veins, to restore the balance.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/611a2bdc630ee45245662672e73cb899.poster.avif?t=1746038470\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/611a2bdc630ee45245662672e73cb899.webm?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3074930/extras/611a2bdc630ee45245662672e73cb899.mp4?t=1746038470\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Eviscerate grotesque abominations</li><li>Choose from an arsenal of potent blood powered weapons</li><li>Reloading your weapon consumes your health, utilize your movement abilities to rush around the arena picking up health that explodes from damaged enemies</li><li>Master each encounter to complete challenges to earn a high rank and unlock upgraded weapons and abilities</li></ul>",
